{"tid":1300870,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"荷蘭留學嘅入嚟","createTime":"2019-07-09T13:18:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T09:29:12.000Z","uid":260375,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"7539556e50f0ad5d8ac51bf20387542ed3f5a9c7","tid":1300870,"uid":260375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T13:18:03.000Z","msg":"以前去過exchange 覺得呢個地方好正 啲鬼仔鬼妹好認真讀書添<br />\n一路都有啲興趣去讀master <br />\n有無荷蘭留學巴絲可以分享下 競爭大唔大？<br />\n如果當地搵工係咪好難呢？<br />\n聽講而家荷蘭好似都無咁歡迎外國人咁"},{"pid":"48ed8a984518037ba0fcb5d2d8710392406deb0f","tid":1300870,"uid":94290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T13:44:53.000Z","msg":"重要!!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n7月10即係聽日截止喇！<br />\n入去推上去呀 <br />\n<br />\n【DQ區選反對確認書】同我入黎填撚左佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1297868\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1297868</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n入去呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9999b296cb5898d9d9d1d6c4c017fef66bc7c7b2","tid":1300870,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T13:47:10.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"eb8097fa2890f62fb6a147c3e25151cccd63afe5","tid":1300870,"uid":46488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T13:49:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https:/